latestPosts.caption:
And as #BiggBossOTT 3 comes to an end, here’s putting through the impeccable journey of our diva. A journey that has been nothing sort of a rollercoaster ride. Playing like a lone wolf, she faced everything in the house with a fierce determination, forming connections that stood out and left a mark on everyone. She fought with unwavering strength, she never shed away from crying and showing her raw emotion, but not even once she entertained the thought of giving up. Through every challenge, she upheld her diva attitude, always ready to give it back when asked to step down.

Misunderstood by many and often labelled as pretentious, she chose to remain unapologetically herself. 

A big big thank you to each one of you, who stood by her through it all, all you #SanaKeSitare you guys are magical ✨ With all your unwavering love and support, our queen has made it. Well indeed Sana’s journey deserved nothing less than a victorious ending. THE TROPHY IS HOME ❤️🤗🥹🧿🏆

#Sanamakbul #Divasana #Actress #TeamSanamakbul #Sanakesitare #Biggbossott3 #Winner
